   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="Edgeworth_Huntington_HM7315_1843_02_17_page01.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <dateline>
                  <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#Edgeworthstown_IE">Edgeworths Town</placeName>
                  <date>Feb<hi rend="superscript">y</hi>. <unclear>17</unclear>
                     <hi rend="superscript">h</hi> 1843</date>
               </dateline>
               <salute>
                  <persName ref="./Personography.xml#WestJ1">Sir</persName>
                  <lb/>
               </salute>
            </opener>
            <p>I would rather give four and<lb/>
               a half percent Cent to you for M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi>. <persName ref="./Personography.xml#DrumX1">
                  <choice>
                     <orig>Drum<lb/>
                  -mond</orig>
                     <reg>Drummond</reg>
                  </choice>
               </persName> than lose the advantage<lb/>
               of dealing with such a respectable<lb/>
               Creditor - I beg to know whether<lb/>
               at this rate of interest <add>namely</add> 4 ½ per Cent<lb/>
               you would lend us<lb/>
               Twelve thousand pounds<lb/>
               provided on having our securities<lb/>
               laid before you by our law<lb/>
                  counsel // <persName ref="./Personography.xml#FoxX1">Fox Esq<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
               </persName>
               <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#Rutland-Square-45_IE 45">Rutland Sq</placeName>
               <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#Dublin_IE">Dublin</placeName>
               <lb/>
               you approve of the same -</p>
            <lb/>
            <closer>
               I am <persName ref="./Personography.xml#WestJ1">Sir</persName>
               <lb/>
               Your Obed<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>. Servant<lb/>
               <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeM1">Maria Edgeworth</persName>
               <lb/>
               <persName ref="./Personography.xml#WestJ1">James Westen</persName>
               <choice>
                  <orig>Esq</orig>
                  <reg>Esquire</reg>
               </choice>
               <lb/>
               <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#Fenchurch-Street-31_ENK">Fenchurch Street</placeName>
               <lb/>
               <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#London_ENK">London</placeName>
               <lb/>
               <pb n="1" facs="Edgeworth_Huntington_HM7315_1843_02_17_page01.jpg"/>
               <address>
